<a href="http://www.chicagonow.com/newsboy/files/2015/11/divine-mercy-confession.jpg"><img src="http://www.chicagonow.com/newsboy/files/2015/11/divine-mercy-confession-300x201.jpg" alt="divine-mercy-confession" width="300" height="201" class="alignright size-medium wp-image-1405" /></a> 

